</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_4abfc5de19138d0df20e9d7e5fc1ea64_1autotoc_md62">
<title>Implementation Note</title><para><computeroutput>GameObjectView</computeroutput> is implemented as a <computeroutput>.h</computeroutput> header instead of a <computeroutput>.ixx</computeroutput> module interface unit due to MSVC Internal Compiler Errors (ICE) when using structured bindings with the <computeroutput>each()</computeroutput> iterator in module contexts.</para>
</sect1>
